title: War of the Roses: Her Knight In Shining Armor or a One Night Fling?
description: Abby was on an awful date when a guy named Michael came and saved her while her date was in the bathroom.  They had a fun night together and now Abby really likes Michael.  She's been trying to go out with him again but he's been pretty distant so now she's wondering if there's someone else in the picture.
